{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think we got a half an hour lunch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember all the SS were sitting around in a perimeter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember watching the SSs, they took out from their packs, you know, their bread and their bacon, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were eating that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, our stomachs we're just groaning from hunger, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were giving scraps to their dogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, the dogs had better food than we had, you know, for sure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was very hard to take.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it was back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we worked till about 6:30 to 7 o'clock, depending, you know, how far away we were from camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nonstop, you know, again, from lunchtime till about 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then it was a march back to camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- the kapos, you know, they drove us-- we had to march in a military fashion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And eventually, you know, we had to sing German songs, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It had to just go like so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it came-- we were back to camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as we came back to camp, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had to clean and polish our shoes and line up for appell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had some, some black stuff, it looked like some grease.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to smear it on our boots, so it looked nice and clean, which was fine, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, you could do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because we had-- where the latrines were, in the barrack, in this big common room, in the middle there was a-- that's where the water taps were, with a trough, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, there were hundreds of-- I don't know, a couple hundred taps there, so that you could wash from either side, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
